headline: Sempra Misses on Q4 Earnings, Lowers '25 EPS Outlook
summary: SRE's Q4 revenues of $3.76 billion increase 7.6% from the year-ago level. The top line, however, misses the Zacks Consensus Estimate by 23.1%.
